## When Auth Fails

1. **First:** Check for existing credentials in the workspace
2. **Second:** Check `~/.config/gcloud/` for cached tokens
3. **Third:** Run the appropriate login command (browser will open)
4. **Fourth:** Inform user only if login window doesn't appear

